B.Nz=new A.Q(B.a7,"Weather is critical to aviation","Weather reports and navigation documents use highly standardized vocabulary. METAR, TAF, NOTAM, and ATIS use specific terms that pilots and controllers must understand instantly.\n\nThis lesson covers the most frequently tested weather and navigation terms.",null,null,null)
B.PT=new A.Q(B.B,"\ud83c\udf26\ufe0f Weather Phenomena","**CAVOK** \u2014 Ceiling And Visibility OK (vis >10km, no cloud below 5000ft, no significant weather)\n**BECMG** \u2014 Becoming (gradual change within a period)\n**TEMPO** \u2014 Temporary fluctuations lasting less than 1 hour\n**CB** \u2014 Cumulonimbus (thunderstorm cloud, avoid by 20nm)\n**TSRA** \u2014 Thunderstorm with rain\n**FG** \u2014 Fog | **BR** \u2014 Mist | **RA** \u2014 Rain | **SN** \u2014 Snow",null,null,null)
